OL,3,CCenter Parcs plans: #400m holiday park
OL,4,Cset to create 1,200 jobs
OL,6,FPlans have been unveiled for a #400m
OL,7,Fholiday park in the Borders which is
OL,8,Fset to create more than 1,200 jobs.
OL,10,FCenter Parcs outlined their vision for
OL,11,Ftheir first Scottish holiday village
OL,12,Fduring an event at Hawick Rugby Club,
OL,13,Fon 5 November 2024.
OL,15,FCenter Parcs aim to submit a planning
OL,16,Fapplication for 700 holiday lodges -
OL,17,Flocated three miles north of Hawick -
OL,18,Fin 2025.
