OL,3,CCenter Parcs plans: #400m holiday park
OL,4,Cset to create 1,200 jobs
OL,6,FThe company believes the investment
OL,7,Fwill provide 'significant benefits'
OL,8,Fincluding more than 1,000 jobs in the
OL,9,Flocal economy.
OL,11,FCenter Parcs says more than 700
OL,12,Fconstruction jobs will be generated
OL,13,Fduring the building phase of the
OL,14,Fproject, as well as 1,200 permanent
OL,15,Fnon-seasonal jobs once the village is
OL,16,Fopen.
OL,18,FColin McKinlay, Chief Executive
OL,19,FOfficer of Center Parcs, believes the
OL,20,Fproposals will "transform leisure and
OL,21,Ftourism" in the Scottish Borders.
