OL,3,CCenter Parcs plans: #400m holiday park
OL,4,Cset to create 1,200 jobs
OL,6,F"Sustainability is core to our values.
OL,7,FIn our three decades of operating in
OL,8,Fthe UK and Ireland, we have
OL,9,Ftransformed areas of commercial
OL,10,Fwoodland into a rich tapestry of flora
OL,11,Fand fauna, considerably enhancing the
OL,12,Fbiodiversity of each village.
OL,14,F"This site gives us the opportunity to
OL,15,Ftake a bold, new approach and create a
OL,16,Fwoodland ourselves, delivering
OL,17,Fsignificant biodiversity net gain and
OL,18,Fplanting thousands of new trees.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
