OL,3,CCenter Parcs plans: #400m holiday park
OL,4,Cset to create 1,200 jobs
OL,6,F"We have already conducted a
OL,7,Fsignificant number of surveys to
OL,8,Fassess the site and we intend to
OL,9,Fcontinue with additional site surveys
OL,10,Fand design development, alongside a
OL,11,Fprogramme of pre-planning application
OL,12,Fconsultation and community engagement."
OL,14,FThe holiday facility will offer a
OL,15,Fvariety of indoor and outdoor
OL,16,Factivities, an Aqua Sana Forest Spa,
OL,17,FCenter Parcs' indoor water park and
OL,18,Fthe Subtropical Swimming Paradise.
