OL,3,CCenter Parcs plans: #400m holiday park
OL,4,Cset to create 1,200 jobs
OL,6,FCenter Parcs aims to deliver
OL,7,F'significant' biodiversity across
OL,8,Ftheir proposed facility by undertaking
OL,9,Fan extensive programme of
OL,10,Fafforestation.
OL,12,FThe holiday site will be located near
OL,13,Fthe A7 trunk road between Hawick and
OL,14,FSelkirk on land currently owned by
OL,15,FBuccleuch Group. The agreed option
OL,16,Fagreement covers around 1,000 acres of
OL,17,Fland - it is expected the developed
OL,18,Fsite will cover 400 acres.
